Trade/Device Name(s): TysonBio AC100 Blood Glucose Monitoring System
TysonBio AC100 Pro Blood Glucose Monitoring System
TysonBio AC200 Blood Glucose Monitoring System
TysonBio AC200 Pro Blood Glucose Monitoring System
Document Summary: FDA 510(k) summary for TysonBio AC100/AC100 Pro/AC200/AC200 Pro Blood Glucose Monitoring Systems for quantitative measurement of glucose in capillary whole blood using electrochemical biosensor technology.
Indications for Use Summary: For quantitative measurement of glucose in fresh capillary whole blood from fingertip, forearm, or palm, intended for self-testing by individuals or multiple-patient use in professional healthcare settings as an aid in monitoring diabetes control; not for diagnosis or neonatal use.
